name: The Lady Mascott - Master of Your Heart
description:
First Piece of Lady Mascott - Chapter 2.

The busy brain behind all.

My mind fluctuates all the time.
The changes is incomprehensible.

Sometimes, it flies to farthest place.
Need to grab it fast and pull it back to present seconds.

None of us is saint.
So, don't try to be a saint.

All of us has a flaw.
So, don't try to be a flawless one.

Understand your heart.
Be master of your own heart.
